originalText.text: Dr. Jack Almeleh is the only therapist I'd ever want in my life.  He is the kind of doctor who really cares about me as a whole person, he has encouraged me in every phase of my life which in the end has also improved my psche.  I had other therapists, but I never really got to accepting myself fully until I was in therapy with Dr. Almeleh.  I'm not sure other therapists encouraged me to be happy, but it never felt so achievable and became such a clear goal until I met Dr. Almeleh & became his patient.  Another positive is that he has been sensitive to my feelings & seems to be perfect about knowing when to be gentle and when to be tough which has also been helpful in motivating me toward a more healthy and happy life.
